original_title: UFC Fight Night 79: Henderson vs. Masvidal
overview: UFC Fight Night 79: Henderson vs. Masvidal was a mixed martial arts event held on November 28, 2015, at Olympic Gymnastics Arena in Seoul, South Korea. A welterweight bout between former WEC and UFC Lightweight Champion Benson Henderson and top contender Jorge Masvidal headlined the event.
title: UFC Fight Night 79: Henderson vs. Masvidal
